sect1:
JSR-109 Endpoints
JSR-109 promotes building portable web services in the J2EE 1.4 environment. It leverages J2EE technologies to provide a standard for developing and deploying web services on the J2EE platform. If you already have followed the Getting Started Chapter you can proceed with EJB endpoints right away.
